WEBVTT

00:00.797 --> 00:01.421
What is this?

00:01.541 --> 00:03.313
This is the plan to help take the company green.

00:03.564 --> 00:03.965
Green?

00:04.065 --> 00:06.289
You mean like light bulbs, recycling?

00:06.563 --> 00:07.598
These guys got everything:...

00:07.719 --> 00:10.989
...data centers, PCs, networking supply chains, top to bottom.

00:11.368 --> 00:11.565
Cute.

00:12.006 --> 00:14.047
But where is the business value in tree hugging?

00:16.840 --> 00:19.157
They could cut our energy cost by as much as 40 percent.

00:19.406 --> 00:19.857
40 percent?

00:20.156 --> 00:20.933
40 percent.

